# PART 15: COMPILATION CHECKLIST — Sections B, F, L, P (100-108)

Apply in this order:

1. **Add helpers** (`default_version()`, `default_hotness()`) to the top of each pipeline — before any struct definitions that reference them via `#[serde(default = "...")]`
